articles.author: Adam S. Levy, Eve Buckland
articles.title: Kevin Costner says estranged wife Christine refuses to move out of home in violation of their prenup - Daily Mail
articles.description: Costner told the court he believes that Baumgartner, 49, is remaining in the home to persuade him to give into 'various financial demands' she is making in the wake of the split.
articles.content:
Kevin Costner has filed legal docs asking a court to compel his estranged wife Christine Baumgartner to leave his home in line with their prenuptial agreement.
